            <header class="section-header ">
                <h2 class="section-title ">
                    <a href="#subheaders">Subheaders</a>
                </h2>
                <p>There are six Winstrap subheader controls. We recommend pairing  <code>type-header1</code> with <code>type-subheader1</code>, <code>type-header2</code> with <code>type-subheader2</code>, etc.</p>
                <p>You can also apply subheaders using the Sass mixin. Subheaders applied using the mixin are not responsive by default. Pass the <code>responsive</code> argument to make them responsive.</p>
            </header>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="type-sh1">Subheader 1</div>
                    <div class="type-sh2">Subheader 2</div>
                    <div class="type-sh3">Subheader 3</div>
                    <div class="type-sh4">Subheader 4</div>
                    <div class="type-sh5">Subheader 5</div>
                    <div class="type-sh6">Subheader 6</div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-24">
